      <span class="Forbes">#ForbesUnder30</span>

      <hr />

      An activist, entrepreneur and actress, Hamilton had rose to stardom in
      2023 thanks to her starring role in her self- directed short film 'Girls
      Just Want to have Fun' and shortly after was casted in OWN Network's
      'Blueberry'. Hamilton will be a reoccuring role on HBO's 'Gossip Girl' as
      Naomi in 2023, and starring alongside Viola Davis in the movie 'Garden of
      Weeds' in 2024. She is the CEO of 'Shadow', a pro bono Therapy directory
      app for BIPOC youth to access affordable services and build a safe
      community.
